name: set_timer_duration
description: Set the duration for the timer by selecting digits.
parameters: {'digit': 'Which digit do you want to add to the timer duration? [1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8, 9, 00, 0]'}

name: delete_last_digit
description: Delete the last digit entered in the timer duration.

name: open_more_options
description: Open additional options for the timer.

name: switch_to_tab
description: Switch to a different tab in the app.
parameters: {'tab': 'Which tab do you want to switch to? [Alarm, Clock, Timer, Stopwatch, Bedtime]'}

name: start_stopwatch
description: Start the stopwatch by clicking the 'Start' button.
